{"tid":1666674,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"蒙面旺角警挑機外籍拍片男 被問為何無證即跳掣叫人「fxxk off！」","createTime":"2019-10-21T05:43:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-21T13:46:36.000Z","uid":19552,"like":278,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":81,"replies":[{"pid":"683a29c6a634c199d1455b1b7a3ad63d811a5142","tid":1666674,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T05:43:23.000Z","msg":"前線防暴警員不時情緒失控，發狂喝罵甚至襲擊在場採訪的記者和圍觀的街坊。在昨日（20日），《眾新聞》拍攝到1名外籍男士，在旺角警署外駐足拍攝防暴警員時，1名蒙面防暴警員突然恫嚇該男士，用英文指「I photo for you if you want」，並指向身後的攝錄機。外籍男士則反駁，問防暴警的委任證在哪裏（Where's your ID？）<br />\n<br />\n另一名蒙面防暴警員按捺不住，爆粗喝罵該外籍男士「Please fxxk off！」外籍男士嘗試安撫警員，希望他冷靜，但該蒙面警員仍然失控，繼續喝罵「Please fxxk off！」該外籍男士其後未有繼續安慰警員並離開。<br />\n警員的英語對答已非首次淪為笑柄。7月27日，有防暴警與外籍記者對話時，一度將「Brian. What's the problem？」聽錯為「Brian Problem」，誤以為是對方全名；9月22日，有防暴警在沙田撤離時，突然轉身以英語要求跟隨拍攝的記者，與他保持「10 Mile（10英里）distan（ce）」（即須後退至大嶼山對開海面），當被記者追問，方澄清是指「10米」；10月1日，防暴警在銅鑼灣瘋狂推撞記者，當被推撞的外籍記者多次要求警員按法例展示其編號時，警員卻支吾以對，不知所云，最後與同袍施施然離開。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20191020/large/1571583348_0844.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20191020%2Flarge%2F1571583348_0844.jpg&h=eeaa408f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n咁有禮貌<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20191021/60176552?itm_campaign=hkad_internal_link&amp;itm_medium=internal&amp;itm_source=hkad_web&amp;itm_content=internal_link_1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191021%2F60176552%3Fitm_campaign%3Dhkad_internal_link%26itm_medium%3Dinternal%26itm_source%3Dhkad_web%26itm_content%3Dinternal_link_1&d=IZFSAkWTwbXSesVVmoeERaVNHo2TAuuzEKoC36QvVjA%3D&h=d3e34ca3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191021%2F60176552%3Fitm_campaign%3Dhkad_internal_link%26itm_medium%3Dinternal%26itm_source%3Dhkad_web%26itm_content%3Dinternal_link_1&h=028f